          <h3>Fast Efficient Online Service</h3>
            <p>
              Mortgages Northern Ireland have moved to providing our clients with a fast efficient online service. Previously like most firms we had been operationg on a face to face basis arranging appointments whereever and whenever was convienient for our clients. This meant that clients had to book time off work to attend appointments or had to drive to a specific location to meet an adviser.
            </p>
            <p>
              The majority of our appointments are now conducted through zoom and phone calls, this means you can quickly book a video chat or a call back in your lunch break or you can sit down at home after work and jump into a video chat with an adviser.
            </p>
            <p>
              We can process an agreement in principle during a video or phone chat which will allow you to move forward in the process confident that your application will be accepted.
            </p>
         </div>
        </div>
